Day 1:
---

## Step 1: Open Spring Initializr

Go to:

  [Spring Initializr](https://start.spring.io/?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

---

## Step 2: Select these options

### Project

  ```text
  Maven
  ```

### Language
  
  ```text
  Java
  ```

### Spring Boot

  Choose stable version.

Example:

  ```text
  3.3.x or 3.4.x
  ```

Do not choose SNAPSHOT.

---

## Step 3: Project Metadata

Fill like this:

```text
    Group: com.tourbooking
    Artifact: tourbooking
    Name: tourbooking
    Description: Tour and Travel Booking System
    Package name: com.tourbooking
    Packaging: Jar
    Java: 17
```

Use **Java 17** because Spring Boot 3 works well with Java 17.

---

## Step 4: Add dependencies

Click **Add Dependencies** and add these:

### Required dependencies

        ```text
        Spring Web
        Spring Data JPA
        MySQL Driver
        Lombok
        Validation
        ```

