## After opening project

First create database in MySQL:

```sql
    CREATE DATABASE tour_booking_system;
```

Then open:

```text
      src/main/resources/application.properties
```

and write:

```properties
        spring.application.name=tourbooking
        
        spring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/tour_booking_system
        spring.datasource.username=root
        spring.datasource.password=your_mysql_password
        
        spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=update
        spring.jpa.show-sql=true
        spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.format_sql=true
        ```

Change this line:

```properties
      spring.datasource.password=your_mysql_password
```

according to your MySQL password.

---

## Then your first coding target

Create these packages:

```text
    controller
    entity
    repository
    service
```

Inside:

```text
    src/main/java/com/tourbooking
```

Like this:

```text
      com.tourbooking
      │
      ├── controller
      ├── entity
      ├── repository
      ├── service
      └── TourbookingApplication.java
      ```

---

## First entity you will create

Create:

```text
    entity/TourPackage.java
```

Then we will make:

```text
      repository/TourPackageRepository.java
      controller/PackageController.java
```

First API target:

```text
      POST /api/admin/packages
      GET  /api/packages
```

